# Telegram contact form (server-side only — never exposed to the client)
# 1. Create a bot via @BotFather and paste its token here.
# 2. Message the bot, then read chat.id from
#    https://api.telegram.org/bot<token>/getUpdates (or use @userinfobot).
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=

# GitHub stats (server-side only). Optional but recommended: raises the GitHub
# API rate limit and powers the build-time snapshot + serverless refresh.
# A classic token needs no scopes for public data; a fine-grained token needs
# public repo read access.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
